## isSet() function

Determines whether the input is `Set` or not.

**Signature:**

```typescript
declare function isSet<T>(value: T): value is T;
```

**Returns:**

value is T

true if the input is `Set`<!-- -->, false otherwise.

## Example


```ts

isSet([])        // false
```
